data.description: *** Move into this home w/ 0.00% down payment! This program is available for Secondary homebuyers too! Loan program is offered through our trusted lending parter for buyers who are purchasing this home as their primary residence *** Look no further! Large 3 level 2 car garage brick home  home is waiting for its new owner - shows beautiful. This well kept home offers 4 bedrooms (2 primary bedrooms / 1 on main level, 1 on upper level 2)  and 2 additional bedrooms. Upper level primary bedroom has 2 walk-in closets and a very spacious primary bath  w/ double vanity, soaking tub and shower. The upper level is perfect for entertaining w/ the open floor plan with the living room, dining area and kitchen combination . You will enjoy cooking in this gourmet kitchen! All high quality Maytag stainless appliances included - double oven, separate built-in microwave, gas cooktop, dishwasher + large pantry. Sip your morning coffee or a glass of wine on the nice balcony.  Since it is an END UNIT natural sunlight fills the house all day.   Parking will never be a problem w/ the large 2 car garages. If you are thinking about additional income - you may Airbnb the main level bedroom w/ en-suite bath for extra $$$.  Lawn maintenance is being provided by the HOA. It is easy living here! The community is located nearby a shopping center that offers many restaurants, stores and entertainment. At the corner a gas station is for your convenience.  Quick access to RT495/95/214/202/4
